{"service_name": "Introduction to Puppet training course", "service_id": "7018178428179325", "company_name": "QA Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     QA Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Introduction to Puppet training course\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    This course covers the basic architecture of Puppet and its associated tools; a major open source systems management tool for centralizing and automating cloud configuration. It aims to prepare key development, engineering, and operations staff to use Puppet to write infrastructure and succeed in a cloud migration.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Introduction to Configuration Management, Puppet Overview, Puppet Components\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Managing assets with Git\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Resources and Providers, Modules and Classes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Using Puppet Without a Master\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Deploying Your Code to the Puppet Master\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Testing Puppet, using Puppet Forge\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Classification, environments and live management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     ERB templates, resources in depth, resource relationships\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     DSL - Domain Specific Language\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Parametrised types, defined resource types and Hiera\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Install and configure Puppet Enterprise\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Install and configure Puppet Agent\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Describe the key components of Puppet including Hiera and Facter\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Write classes comprising desired resources for a node\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Test their Puppet configurations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Use Puppet to configure multiple web servers\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a31148 per person\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Education pricing available\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Other\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/579507/7018178428179325-pricing-document-2015-10-06-1148.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/579507/7018178428179325-service-definition-document-2015-10-01-1345.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/579507/7018178428179325-terms-and-conditions-2015-10-01-1345.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and condi